        "author_role": "OWNER",
        "timestamp": "2018-05-08 12:40:37.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\nMayank, this is necessary, trust me.  I explored that option you mentioned first thing but things don't work properly.  The operation of PAP and PDP is more complicated that just being able to ping each other as PAP keeps a pre-provisioned whitelist which has to to match the full qualified domain name.   There are more complicated possibilities to modify policy/engine repo, or more involved hacking on helm scripts.   This is the simplest solution that works.",
